00:04:03.160 --> 00:04:04.160
Boy: Yeah.

00:04:04.160 --> 00:04:05.160
Marcus: A modern day poet.

00:04:05.160 --> 00:04:06.160
Boy: Yeah, you could say that.

00:04:06.160 --> 00:04:08.160
