00:04:54.160 --> 00:04:57.160
and just went in there and kicked everybody's arse.

00:04:57.160 --> 00:05:01.160
Fuckin’ wicked, man. I saw the movie. Bad! What?

00:05:01.160 --> 00:05:05.160
